Many years of challenges and many months of talks resulted in the decision by Prince Harry and his wife Meghan to give up their place as senior members of the royal family. In a speech at a dinner for one of his charities, the prince said the decision to step back was not made lightly. He assured the attendees they would continue serving theirÂ  charities, while seeking a more peaceful life. An emotional Harry expressed gratitude for the support he and his family have received.